Creating Server
--------------
1. we have to  craete package.json

commands for creating package.json
npm init

2.create entry point file (index.js)

3.we have to install express in the serve 
commands for installing
npm i express

4.import express inside index.js file
 using require

5.we have to create server app using express

6.setup port for serve app
 method used here is "listen"

7. run this using node 

8.to resolve client http request

1xx-------information
2xx-------success
3xx--------redirection
4xx--------

to connect mongo db with server
the library used is mongoose(to connect mongodb to server)

to install mongoose ----npm i mongoose in the terminal of bank server.